sub_title: BSc Business Analytics Student | Scholar | Tutor at Maastricht University
summary: As a highly driven Business Analytics student at Maastricht University, I am proud to be part of the top 5% of my cohort. My passion for learning and growth extends beyond academics, as I actively engage in numerous associations such as Beta Gamma Sigma Honours Society, Women in Business, SCOPE, and Sigma Investments. Additionally, I contribute as a consultant at Maastricht Student Consulting, applying my analytical skills to real-world business challenges. I am honoured to be a scholarship recipient from the Hanns-Seidel-Stiftung.
